 Gusman\n*2002: Sidney Gusman\n*2003: Sidney Gusman\n*2004: Sidney Gusman\n*2005: Sidney Gusman\n*2006: Sidney Gusman\n*2007: Sidney Gusman\n*2008: Paulo Ramos\n*2009: Rog\u00e9rio de Campos\n*2010: S\u00e9rgio Codespoti\n\n=== Best Editor ===\n*1989: Jal and Gualberto Costa\n*1990: Rog\u00e9rio de Campos\n\n=== Best Editorial Cartoonist ===\n*1997: [[Angeli (cartoonist)|Angeli]]\n*1998: [[Angeli (cartoonist)|Angeli]]\n*1999: [[Angeli (cartoonist)|Angeli]]\n*2000: [[Angeli (cartoonist)|Angeli]]\n*2001: [[Angeli (cartoonist)|Angeli]]\n*2002: [[Angeli (cartoonist)|Angeli]]\n*2003: [[Angeli (cartoonist)|Angeli]]\n*2004: [[Angeli (cartoonist)|Angeli]]\n*2005: [[Angeli (cartoonist)|Angeli]]\n*2006: [[Angeli (cartoonist)|Angeli]]\n*2007: [[Angeli (cartoonist)|Angeli]]\n*2008: [[Angeli (cartoonist)|Angeli]]\n*2009: [[Angeli (cartoonist)|Angeli]]\n*2010: [[Angeli (cartoonist)|Angeli]]\n*2011: [[Angeli (cartoonist)|Angeli]]\n*2012: [[Angeli (cartoonist)|Angeli]]\n\n=== Best Foreign Penciller ===\nThe award considers the Brazilian edition of their works.\n*1989: [[Frank Miller (comics)|Frank Miller]] {{flagicon|USA}}\n*1990: [[Dave Stevens]] {{flagicon|USA}}\n*1991: [[Kent Williams (artist)|Kent Williams]] {{flagicon|USA}}\n*1992: [[Katsuhiro Otomo]] {{flagicon|JPN}}\n*1993: [[Todd McFarlane]] {{flagicon|CAN}}\n*1994: [[John Romita Jr.]] {{flagicon|USA}}\n*1995: [[Ivo Milazzo]] {{flagicon|ITA}}\n*1996: [[George Pratt (artist)|George Pratt]] {{flagicon|USA}}\n*1997: [[Frank Miller (comics)|Frank Miller]] {{flagicon|USA}}\n*1998: [[Alex Ross]] {{flagicon|USA}}\n*1999: [[Will Eisner]] {{flagicon|USA}}\n*2000: [[Jeff Smith (cartoonist)|Jeff Smith]] {{flagicon|USA}}, for ''[[Bone (comics)|Bone]]''\n*2001: [[Ivo Milazzo]] {{flagicon|ITA}}, for ''[[Ken Parker (comics)|Ken Parker]]''\n*2002: [[Ivo Milazzo]] {{flagicon|ITA}}, for ''[[Ken Parker (comics)|Ken Parker]]''\n*2003: [[Takehiko Inoue]] {{flagicon|JPN}}, for ''[[Vagabond (manga)|Vagabond]]''\n*2004: [[Lorenzo Mattotti]] {{flag