etterer ===\n*1999: Lilian Mitsunaga\n\n=== Best New Talent (Penciller) ===\nUntil 2010, this category was called \"Revelation Penciller\".\n*1990: Osvaldo Pavanelli\n*1991: Jaca\n*1992: Kipper\n*1993: MZK\n*1994: Guazzelli\n*1995: Luciano Queiroz\n*1996: Dalcio\n*1997: Lelis\n*1998: Alan Sieber\n*1999: Luciano Lagares\n*2000: [[F\u00e1bio Moon]] and [[Gabriel B\u00e1]], for ''10 P\u00e3ezinhos''\n*2001: [[F\u00e1bio Yabu]], for ''[[Combo Rangers]]''\n*2002: Samuel Casal\n*2003: Andr\u00e9 Kitagawa, for ''Front''\n*2004: Andr\u00e9 Bueno, for ''Front''\n*2005: Rafael Sica\n*2006: [[Julia Bax]], for ''Kaos'' and ''Quebra-Queixo''\n*2007: F\u00e1bio Lyra, for ''Mosh!''\n*2008: Jozz, for ''Zine Royale''\n*2009: Hemeterio, for ''Chibata! - Jo\u00e3o C\u00e2ndido e a revolta que abalou o Brasil''\n*2010: [[Gustavo Duarte]], for ''C\u00f3!''\n*2011: Felipe Massafera, for ''Jambocks''\n*2012: Magno Costa and Marcelo Costa, for ''Oeste Vermelho'' and ''Matin\u00ea''\n*2013: Pedro Franz, for ''Suburbia''\n*2014: Lu Cafaggi, for ''[[Turma da M\u00f4nica - La\u00e7os]]''\n*2015: Felipe Nunes, for ''Klaus''\n*2016: Camila Torrano, for ''F\u00e1bulas'' and ''Spam''\n*2017: Mika Takahashi, for ''Al\u00e9m dos Trilhos''\n*2018: Bruno Seelig\n*2019: Melissa Garabeli, for ''Saudade''\n\n=== Best New Talent (Writer) ===\nUntil 2010, this category was called \"Revelation Writer\".\n*2007: Daniel Esteves, for ''Front n\u00ba 17''\n*2008: Cadu Sim\u00f5es, for ''Homem-Grilo'', ''Nova H\u00e9lade'' and ''Garagem Herm\u00e9tica''\n*2009: Olintho Gadelha, for ''Chibata! - Jo\u00e3o C\u00e2ndido e a revolta que abalou o Brasil''\n*2010: Alex Mir, for ''Orix\u00e1s'', ''Subversos'' and ''Tempestade cerebral''\n*2011: [[Daniel Galera]], for ''Cachalote''\n*2012: Vitor Cafaggi, for ''Valente para sempre'' and ''Duo.tone''\n*2013: Raphael Fernandes, for ''Ida e Volta'' and ''Ditadura no Ar n\u00ba 2''\n*2014: Pedro Cobiaco, for ''Hermat\u00e3''\n*2015: [[Bianca Pinheiro]], for ''Dora'' and ''Bear''\n*2016: Z\u00e9 Wellington, for ''Steampunk Ladies - Vingan\u00e7a a Vapor''\n*2017: Wagner Willian, for ''Bulldogma''\n*2018: Carol Pimentel\n*2019: J\u00e9ssica Groke, for ''Me Leve Quando Sair''\n\n=== Best Penciller ===\n*1989: [[Alain Voss]]\n*1990: Lu\u00eds Gustavo\n*1991: [[Laerte Coutinho]]\n*1992: Luiz G\u00ea\n*1993: Octavio Cariello\n*1994: [[Louren\u00e7o Mutarelli]]\n*1995: Flavio Colin\n*1996: [[Angeli (cartoonist)|Angeli]]\n*1997: [[Mike Deodato]]\n*1998: Lelis\n*1999: Edgar Vasques\n*2000: [[Louren\u00e7o Mutarelli]], for ''O dobro de cinco''<ref name=\"Reference2000\">{{cite web |url=http://omelete.uol.com.br/quadrinhos/12o-trofeu-hq-mix-e-os-melhores-de-99/ |title=12\u00ba Trof\u00e9u HQ Mix e os melhores de 99 |publisher=[[Omelete]] |date=July 21, 2000}}</ref>\n*2001: [[Louren\u00e7o Mutarelli]], for ''O rei do ponto''<ref name=\"Reference2001\">{{cite web |url=http://www.universohq.com/quadrinhos/n13092001_05.cfm |title=Equipe do Universo HQ ganha dois trof\u00e9us HQ Mix |publisher=Universo HQ |date=September 13, 2001 |access-date=March 29, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130328124659/http://www.universohq.com/quadrinhos/n13092001_05.cfm |archive-date=March 28, 2013 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n*2002: [[Louren\u00e7o Mutarelli]], for ''A soma de tudo''<ref name=\"Reference2002\">{{cite web |url=http://www.universohq.com/quadrinhos/n11092002_04.cfm |title=Equipe do Universo HQ \u00e9 biampe\u00e3 do HQ Mix em duas categorias |publisher=Universo HQ |date=September 11, 2002 |access-date=March 29, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130327103450/http://www.universohq.com/quadrinhos/n11092002_04.cfm |archive-date=March 27, 2013 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n*2003: [[Laerte Coutinho]], for ''Deus 2'' and ''Classificados 2''<ref name=\"Reference2003\">{{cite web |url=http://www.universohq.com/quadrinhos/2003/n10062003_06.cfm |title=Equipe do Universo HQ conquista tricampeonato do HQ Mix em duas categorias |publisher=Universo HQ |date=June 10, 2003 |access-date=March 29, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130328164358/http://www.universohq.com/quadrinhos/2003/n10062003_06.cfm |archive-date=March 28, 2013 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n*2004: Samuel Casal, for ''Front''<ref name=\"Reference2004\">{{cite web |url=http://www.universohq.com/quadrinhos/2004/n23062004_01.cfm |title=Universo HQ \u00e9 tetracampe\u00e3o do HQ Mix em duas categorias |publisher=Universo HQ |date=June 23, 2004 |access-date=March 29, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100203184649/http://universohq.com/quadrinhos/2004/n23062004_01.cfm |archive-date=February 3, 2010 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n*2005: [[F\u00e1bio Moon]] and [[Gabriel B\u00e1]], for ''10 P\u00e3ezinhos - cr\u00edtica''<ref name=\"Reference2005\">{{cite web |url=http://www.universohq.com/quadrinhos/2005/n18072005_01.cfm |title=Universo HQ Pentacampe\u00e3o: confira os resultados do 17\u00b0 HQ Mix |publisher=Universo HQ |date=July 18, 2005 |access-date=March 29, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100202005522/http://universohq.com/quadrinhos/2005/n18072005_01.cfm |archive-date=February 2, 2010 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n*2006: Spacca, for ''Sant\u00f4 e os pais da avia\u00e7\u00e3o''<ref name=\"Reference2006\">{{cite web |url=http://www.universohq.com/quadrinhos/2006/n05062006_04.cfm |title=Universo HQ e Sidney Gusman s\u00e3o hexacampe\u00f5es do HQ Mix |publisher=Universo HQ |date=June 5, 2006 |access-date=March 29, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110107180006/http://www.universohq.com/quadrinhos/2006/n05062006_04.cfm |archive-date=January 7, 2011 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n*2007: [[F\u00e1bio Moon]] and [[Gabriel B\u00e1]], for ''Mesa para dois''<ref name=\"Reference2007\">{{cite web |url=http://www.universohq.com/quadrinhos/2007/n02072007_10.cfm |title=Pela s\u00e9tima vez consecutiva, Universo HQ e Sidney Gusman ganham o HQ Mix |publisher=Universo HQ |date=July 2, 2007 |access-date=March 29, 2018