endetta]]''), by [[Alan Moore]] and [[David Lloyd (comics)|David Lloyd]] (Via Lettera)\n*2000: ''Gen - p\u00e9s descal\u00e7os - uma hist\u00f3ria de Hiroshima'' (''[[Barefoot Gen|Hadashi no Gen]]''), by [[Keiji Nakazawa]] (Conrad)\n*2001: ''Gen - p\u00e9s descal\u00e7os - uma hist\u00f3ria de Hiroshima'' (''[[Barefoot Gen|Hadashi no Gen]]''), by [[Keiji Nakazawa]] (Conrad)\n*2002: ''Pr\u00edncipe Valente XVI - uma nova era'' (''[[Prince Valiant]]''), by [[Hal Foster]] (Opera Graphica)\n*2003: ''[[Fritz the Cat]]'', by [[Robert Crumb]] (Conrad)\n\n=== Best Classic Comic Book ===\n*1989: ''[[Spirit (comics)|Spirit]]'', by [[Will Eisner]]\n*1990: ''Cripta do Terror''\n*1991: ''[[Spirit (comics)|Spirit]]'', by [[Will Eisner]]\n*1995: ''Cole\u00e7\u00e3o Invictus'', by many authors (Nova Sampa)\n*2003: ''Novos Deuses'' (''[[New Gods]]''), by [[Jack Kirby]] (Opera Graphica)\n\n=== Best Classic Publication ===\nThis category was merged from \"Best Classic Album\" and \"Best Classic Comic Book\".\n*2004: ''[[Zap Comix]]'', by [[Robert Crumb]] (Conrad)\n*2005: ''Todo Perer\u00ea'' #3, by [[Ziraldo]] (Salamandra)\n*2006: ''[[Maus]]'', by [[Art Spiegelman]] (Cia. das Letras)\n*2007: ''Corto Maltese - a balada do mar salgado'' (''[[Corto Maltese|Una ballata del mare salato]]''), by [[Hugo Pratt]] (Pixel)\n*2008: ''Um contrato com Deus e outras hist\u00f3rias de corti\u00e7o'' (''[[A Contract with God]]''), by [[Will Eisner]] (Devir)\n*2009: ''Che - os \u00faltimos dias de um her\u00f3i'' (''[[Vida del Che]]''),  by [[H\u00e9ctor Oesterheld]], [[Alberto Breccia]] and [[Enrique Breccia]] (Conrad)\n*2010: ''Peanuts completo - 1950 a 1952'' (''[[The Complete Peanuts]]''), by [[Charles Schulz]] (L&PM)\n*2011: ''Peanuts completo'' (''[[The Complete Peanuts]]''), by [[Charles Schulz]] (L&PM)\n*2012: ''[[Arzach]]'', by [[Jean Giraud|Moebius]] (Nemo)\n*2013: ''Diomedes - a trilogia do acidente'', by [[Louren\u00e7o Mutarelli]] (Quadrinhos na Cia)\n*2014: ''Fradim'', 'by [[Henfil]] (Henfil - Educa\u00e7\u00e3o e Sustentabilidade)\n*2015: ''A Saga do Monstro do P\u00e2ntano \u2013 Volumes 1 a 3'' (''[[Swamp Thing|Saga of the Swamp Thing]]''), by many authors (Panini)\n*2016: ''Zod\u00edaco Premium'', by Jayme Cortez (Opera Graphica)\n*2017: ''Sharaz-de - Contos de As Mil e Uma Noites - Volume 1'' (''Sharaz-de''), by [[Sergio Toppi]] (Figura)\n*2018: ''[[Akira (manga)|Akira]]'', by [[Katsuhiro Otomo]] (JBC)\n*2019: ''[[Akira (manga)|Akira 2]]'', by [[Katsuhiro Otomo]] (JBC)\n\n=== Best Comic Strips Publication ===\n*2004: ''[[N\u00edquel N\u00e1usea|N\u00edquel N\u00e1usea - nem tudo que balan\u00e7a cai]]'', by Fernando Gonsales (Devir)\n*2005: ''[[N\u00edquel N\u00e1usea|N\u00edquel N\u00e1usea - v\u00e1 pentear macacos]]'', by Fernando Gonsales (Devir)\n*2006: ''[[N\u00edquel N\u00e1usea|N\u00edquel N\u00e1usea - a perereca da vizinha]]'', by Fernando Gonsales (Devir)\n*2007: ''[[N\u00edquel N\u00e1usea|N\u00edquel N\u00e1usea - t\u00e9dio no chiqueiro]]'', by Fernando Gonsales (Devir)\n*2008: ''O mundo \u00e9 m\u00e1gico - Calvin e Haroldo'' (''[[List of Calvin and Hobbes books|It's a Magical World]]''), by [[Bill Watterson]] (Conrad)\n*2009: ''[[N\u00edquel N\u00e1usea|N\u00edquel N\u00e1usea - em boca fechada n\u00e3o entra mosca]]'', by Fernando Gonsales (Devir)\n*2010: ''[[N\u00edquel N\u00e1usea|N\u00edquel N\u00e1usea - um tigre, dois tigres, tr\u00eas tigres]]'', by Fernando Gonsales (Devir)\n*2011: ''[[N\u00edquel N\u00e1usea|N\u00edquel N\u00e1usea - a vaca foi pro brejo]]'', by Fernando Gonsales (Devir)\n*2012: ''[[Macanudo|Macanudo 4]]'', by [[Liniers (cartoonist)|Liniers]] (Zarabatana)\n*2013: ''Valente para todas'', by Vitor Cafaggi (independent)\n*2014: ''Valente por op\u00e7\u00e3o'', by Vitor Cafaggi (Panini)\n*2015: ''A Vida com Logan - para ler no sof\u00e1'', by Flavio Soares (Jupati Books)\n*2016: ''Will Tirando'', by Will Leite (independent)\n*2017: ''Quadrinhos dos Anos 10'', by Andr\u00e9 Dahmer (Quadrinhos na Cia)\n*2018: