io Pindura 2011'', by many authors (Pegasus Alado)\n*2012: ''[[List of Monica's Gang printed media|MSP Novos 50 - Mauricio de Sousa por 50 Novos Artistas]]'', by many authors (Panini)\n*2013: ''[[Graphic MSP]]'', by many authors (Panini)\n*2014: ''Cole\u00e7\u00e3o Moebius'', by [[Jean Giraud|Moebius]] (Nemo)\n*2015: ''Humor Paulistano - A Experi\u00eancia da Circo Editorial, 1984-1995'', by Toninho Mendes, organizer (SESI-SP)\n*2016: ''O Fabuloso Quadrinho Brasileiro de 2015'', by [[Rafael Coutinho]], Clarice Reichstul and \u00c9rico Assis, organizers (Veneta)\n*2017: ''A Liga Extraordin\u00e1ria - Dossi\u00ea Negro - Edi\u00e7\u00e3o de Luxo Limitada'' (''[[The League of Extraordinary Gentlemen: Black Dossier]]''), by [[Alan Moore]] and [[Kevin O'Neill (comics)|Kevin O'Neill]] (Devir)\n*2018: ''Os Mundos de Jack Kirby - um tributo ao rei dos quadrinhos'', by many authors ([[Guia dos Quadrinhos]])\n*2019: ''A Arte de Charlie Chan Hock Chye'' (''[[The Art of Charlie Chan Hock Chye]]''), by [[Sonny Liew]] (Pipoca & Nanquim)\n\n=== Best Erotic Publication ===\nUntil 2001, this category was called \"Best Erotic Album\".\n*1989: ''As 110 p\u00edlulas'' (''Le 110 pillole''), by [[Roberto Raviola|Magnus]] (Martins Fontes)\n*1990: ''[[Necron (comics)|Necron]]'', by [[Roberto Raviola|Magnus]] (L&PM)\n*1991: ''[[Little Ego]]'', by [[Vittorio Giardino|Giardino]] (Martins Fontes) / ''Sampa Graphic Album'' #2: ''Fetichast - prov\u00edncias do desejo'', by Jos\u00e9 M\u00e1rcio Nicolosi (Sampa) / ''O Clic 2'' (''[[Click (comics)|Il gioco 2]]''), by [[Milo Manara]] (Martins Fontes)\n*1992: ''[[Druuna]]'', by [[Paolo Eleuteri Serpieri]]\n*1993: ''[[Druuna]]'', by [[Paolo Eleuteri Serpieri]]\n*1994: ''Kama Sutra'', by [[Milo Manara]] (L&PM)\n*2001: ''Vol\u00fapia'', by Julio Shimamoto (Opera Graphica)\n*2007: ''[[Valentina (comics)|Valentina - Crepax 65-66]]'', by [[Guido Crepax]] (Conrad)\n*2008: ''[[Lost Girls (graphic novel)|Lost Girls]]'', by [[Alan Moore]] e [[Melinda Gebbie]]